commander.description: The card that is the Commander in this deck. See the {{link@Card@/data-models/card/}} data model.

fileName.description: File name for the deck. Combines the {{code@name}} and {{code@code}} fields to avoid namespace collisions.

sideBoard.description: The cards in the side-board. See the {{link@Card@/data-models/card/}} data model.

releaseDate.description: Release date in {{link@ISO 8601@https://www.iso.org/iso-8601-date-and-time-format.html}} format for the set. Returns {{code@null}} if the set was not formally released as a product.
